  "prompt": "How long HCL technology takes to give offer letter after document uploading round for experience?",
  "response": "The timeframe for receiving an offer letter from HCL Technologies after the document uploading round can vary based on several factors, including the specific role, the number of candidates being processed, and the internal hiring procedures of the company. Typically, candidates might expect to wait anywhere from a few days to a couple of weeks for communication regarding an offer. \n\nIf you are looking for precise information related to your application status, it's best to reach out directly to your HCL recruiter or the HR department for the most accurate updates.",
